     <h1>Welcome to the ATP Champion Tracker!</h1>

  <p>This app allows you to record and manage ATP tennis champions by tournament, year, level, and final score.</p>

  <h2>How to Use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Sign up or log in using the authentication forms</li>
    <li>Navigate to “All Champions” to see current entries</li>
    <li>Click “New Entry” to add a tournament result</li>
    <li>Use “Edit” or “Delete” to modify your data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
  <p>Node.js, Express, MongoDB, EJS, HTML/CSS</p>


